latestIgtvVideos.title: L'Oréal Professionnel | Tecni Art. New launch | Hairstyling products | Time
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@lorealpro_education_india @lorealpro @lorealindia @shwetasahni.pro @reetudang09 @prashant.hiremath 
L'oreal Professionnel has come up with some new range of hairstyling products for all the hair lovers.

4 new products in the Techi art. range

*Tecni Art savage panache*
-It is a hairspray 
-can be used pre styling or post styling 
- has a hold factor of 4
- does not leave any residue on the hair
- also can be used as a dry shampoo for oily hair roots

*Tecni Art pli*
- it is a thermal protection spray
- it is to be used pre styling, very similar to CONSTRUCTOR from L'oreal 
- has a hold factor of 4
- it holds the styling for very long without damaging the hair 

*Tecni Art Transformer*
- it is mousse that trasforms into a gel
- can be used pre styling or post styling 
- has a hold factor of 3
- ideal for thick unmanageable hair
- gives a wet look 
- use very little product or else there will be a buildup of product in the hair

*Tecni Art Ring Light*
- it is a shine spray 
- it needs to be used post styling 
- gives immense shine on apply to the hair

All products should be available in any Loreal Professionnel Salon.

L'Oréal Professionnel | Tecni Art. New launch | Hairstyling products | Time Machine Salon 9702402402
